     C* C5: TIME stores hhmmss into TOD (0 decimals, always 0..235959).
     C* Exit 1 if TOD is in range (sanity check only -- non-deterministic
     C* value can't be exactly asserted).
     C                     TIME           TOD              
     C           TOD       COMP 0                      10  
     C           TOD       COMP 235959               11    
     C  N10N11             Z-ADD1         RPGRET           
